{"tid":922312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啲肥人真係好噁心","createTime":"2018-11-30T09:26:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T09:48:54.000Z","uid":135406,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"07de6a87fd7cb77cab37c36200c208a114fb9fed","tid":922312,"uid":135406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢肥底瘦底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，明明自己對個身體唔負責仲要大條道理，你肥只係因為你食太多又唔撚運動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個人唔係有病嘅話，有做運動肥極有個譜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，就算食得多都係變大隻肥，唔係好似啲肥人咁啲肉鬆拋拋，其實你班肥人有冇諗過自己係唔需要咁多食物㗎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa723463944463c646e285c67b39b97482012fc0","tid":922312,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:28:33.000Z","msg":"失敗者總有籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bdc327a0b21d977d6f91e93018b770e8ecb93f","tid":922312,"uid":160110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:32:56.000Z","msg":"咪就係 我以前小學唔識做運動 變左全校最肥。日日比人笑。後尾開始打籃球 拉高返成個人。就無比人笑過。e家做埋gym。就算點食都唔會肥返 真係爽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8beab30392f814f3ab195ff7755dc2ea1cde0034","tid":922312,"uid":1964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"Fcb有follow啲女仔page<br />\n有時見到咩棉花糖女孩衣著配搭 豐滿也能穿得很可愛（類似字眼）<br />\n第一，肥就肥啦，乜撚嘢棉花糖女孩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二，賤肉橫生咁，點着都唔會同可愛扯上關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有，byebye肉、大肚腩、象腿唔撚好自稱肉感啦<br />\n大波大籮先係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aeceb0803066ac20068da69151393ebd37f160c","tid":922312,"uid":90392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:40:29.000Z","msg":"其實肥人唔惹到其他人, 無咩問題, <br />\n但自己擋住路, 人地過佢都要俾說話人聽...<br />\n肥無罪, 格衰又唔知自己阻人真係大罪, 吔屎啦肥佬肥婆!"},{"pid":"90b9fa936362330496161267f7ce31b57d9e8c3a","tid":922312,"uid":135406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8beab30392f814f3ab195ff7755dc2ea1cde0034","tid":922312,"uid":1964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"Fcb有follow啲女仔page<br />\n有時見到咩棉花糖女孩衣著配搭 豐滿也能穿得很可愛（類似字眼）<br />\n第一，肥就肥啦，乜撚嘢棉花糖女孩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二，賤肉橫生咁，點着都唔會同可愛扯上關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有，byebye肉、大肚腩、象腿唔撚好自稱肉感啦<br />\n大波大籮先係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:48:54.000Z","msg":"就係呢啲人搞到啲肥人咁有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}